    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, but it's a bit high-level. could you dig deeper into the economic and social aspects? specifically, my students need to understand the arguments regarding the impact on wages for low-skilled workers and how unregulated migration might affect social cohesion or public infrastructure. get into the nitty-gritty of those points so they can handle a really tough rebuttal during the round.",
